productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Krista has one of these. She works as a salesman and she says it looks soapy.
My co-worker Tyron has one of these. He says it looks stout.
The box this comes in is 5 kilometer by 6 meter and weights 20 ounce!
My chicken loves to play with it.
I saw one of these in French Southern and Antarctic Lands and I bought one.
